HEADWORD: Sportsmanship
<hw>Sports"man*ship</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The practice of sportsmen;
skill in field sports.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- conduct becoming to one participating in sport or competition, as
